{"tid":1602392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"問毒撚，十月一日放假有乜做?","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:34:19.000Z","uid":249170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4873b9aebc921f5a902d819f989a87503d29a5a7","tid":1602392,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-好愛香港<br />\n-冇父幹<br />\n-揾既錢儲成世都買唔到樓<br />\n-樣衰，窮肥矮毒柒蠢<br />\n-冇女<br />\n-好憎大陸狗落黎拎福利</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我十月一號應該做乜?<br />\n應否果日用生命光復這香港<br />\n有上述特徵既人會唔會一齊企出黎<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c5db755e56b158ccb706d9740fe40f5aedf9b23c","tid":1602392,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我已經輸到冇野好輸，得條命，驚乜撚</span>"},{"pid":"e649317c77e1666b8a4a8ea5e2271883aa7da329","tid":1602392,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"245e2c75330fe70ffa46653590bb44be2bbbbb6e","tid":1602392,"uid":34093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"同巴打差唔多<br />\n我等緊所謂和理非突破哂底線<br />\n然後終極一戰"},{"pid":"969883e725c899ee6c77240b0047dc71fffb7e1b","tid":1602392,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"為失散仔女送上麻包袋"},{"pid":"50e8c26cf558fe0317bca46ea4497b8f3817be82","tid":1602392,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"多謝上面回覆<br />\n<br />\n推"}]}